title: Smoke Signals (1998) Comedy-Drama
description:
Young Indian man Thomas is a nerd in his reservation, wearing oversize glasses 
and telling everyone stories no-one wants to hear. 

His parents died in a fire in 1976, and Thomas was saved by Arnold. Arnold soon left his family (and his tough 
son Victor), and Victor hasn't seen his father for 10 years. When Victor hears 
Arnold has died, Thomas offers him funding for the trip to get Arnold's remains, but only if Thomas will also go with him. Thomas and Victor hit the road.
